  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5098772">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5098772/" class="title-link">何为中国？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5098772"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-09-16"
      class="main-meta">2011-09-16 15:11:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5098772_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  葛兆光说古代中国以文化认同我深以为然，然对其论述宋代中国出现疆域意识论证中国民族国家形成不同于西方却有不同看法   所谓民族国家，首先发端于英法资产阶级革命，尤其是法国大革命之后，其趋向有对内对外两个方面，对内体现在以国民意识取代臣民，以国民权力取代国王和贵族...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5098772/#comments">(43回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
